{"tid":1383330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"#集中討論罷工文宣啦好嗎？？？","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:14:36.000Z","uid":100372,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e66d616a16a74e69dd9f1a0d836a1c4a8e315e","tid":1383330,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:17:14.000Z","msg":"我明白大家睇到有post出話見到有後生冇錢食飯好心up<br />\n<strong><em>但助養有一定風險</em></strong><br />\n比狗黎約比咩飯劵 約食飯黎捉人<br />\n或者有啲有心人有位入 去煩9啲絲打 <br />\n真係有心嘅 不如直接買物資 <br />\n或者直接買食物好過啦 <br />\n諗深一層都知助養 咩飯卷 餐廳合作 <br />\n實行難度極高同費時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你搞得黎場運動都唔知發展到咩局勢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集中火力打主線任務啦</span></ins></strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而且所有出post助養個啲全部都係P牌</span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家理智少少 有心幫 唔一定要直接比錢/請食飯<br />\n可以有其他方法 冷靜分析 唔好比人帶風向啦 唔該各位手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月5號全民大罷工<br />\n先係主線任務啊</span></ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"07ebd6677f0cb8110cc1e7dd9bb4d604395e8651","tid":1383330,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b790174bd58f2df6dad0cc0a1b0e082ee7604562","tid":1383330,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fd1aa81c60e59cc74d4b0283ee0d6dbd82267073","tid":1383330,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae846ab764abd7d9f8820ce0854083fd4d04673e","tid":1383330,"uid":100372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" clas